have an entire new set.<EOS> 

Do you raid a mosque, which serves as a terrorist ammunition storage?<EOS> Do you
return fire, if you are attacked from a hospital?<EOS> Do you storm a church taken
over by terrorists who took the priests hostages?<EOS> Do you search every ambulance
