broke, I feel bad it was their opening!<EOS> Anyway, once that is fixed, this place
will be amazing.<EOS> Drinks were awesome, prices reasonable, and staff friendly.<EOS>
This is an awesome date spot that the area SERIOUSLY needs.<EOS> Check out The Willow
Lounge, youll be happy!<EOS> 

Its been a few years since I have been to Ipanema.<EOS> But my wife and I first went
